{"defs":[{"body":[],"doc":"Writer (D) \u2014 owns FS:write_file with explicit delegation.","effects":{"allow":[{"delegation":"explicit","op":"FS:write_file","reversible":false}]},"grants":["FS:write_file"],"name":"write_output","op":"def"},{"body":[{"fn":"write_output","op":"call"}],"doc":"Processor (C) \u2014 forgot to add 'grants': ['FS:write_file']. FC-E010 fires here.","effects":{"allow":[{"delegation":"explicit","op":"FS:write_file","reversible":false}]},"name":"run_pipeline","op":"def"},{"body":[{"fn":"run_pipeline","op":"call"}],"doc":"Analyzer (B) \u2014 properly declares grants.","effects":{"allow":[{"delegation":"explicit","op":"FS:write_file","reversible":false}]},"grants":["FS:write_file"],"name":"generate_report","op":"def"},{"body":[{"fn":"generate_report","op":"call"}],"doc":"Reporter (A) \u2014 properly declares grants.","effects":{"allow":[{"delegation":"explicit","op":"FS:write_file","reversible":false}]},"grants":["FS:write_file"],"name":"write_summary","op":"def"}],"doc":"4-agent delegation chain demo \u2014 Processor (C) is missing 'grants'.\n\nChain: Reporter (A) \u2192 Analyzer (B) \u2192 Processor (C) \u2192 Writer (D)\n\nWriter (D) still holds FS:write_file with delegation='explicit'.\nProcessor (C) forgot to declare 'grants', so when check_program() inspects\nthe C\u2192D call it raises FC-E010 (ExplicitDelegationViolation).\n\nZone of Indifference: without 'grants' enforcement, irreversible filesystem\naccess could silently flow from D up through C to any caller of C.","kind":"delegation-chain","nail":"0.9.0"}
